name: SAFU
description: "Funds are SAFU" is more than just a meme—it’s a bold promise, a rallying call, and a mission to rebuild trust and integrity on the BNB Chain. SAFU is carefully designed with robust security measures, full transparency, and a genuinely community-driven mindset. No rugs, no dev tricks—just authentic protection for degens tired of getting burned. We're cleaning up the chain, one block at a time. SAFU isn’t just safe—it’s the future we deserve. Together, let’s make BNB Chain truly great again.
